reviews.review_text: THE NASTY COP'S OF NASSAU THIS WAS THE LAST TIME I MADE IT OUT NASSAU COUNTY FOR GOOD REASON AND UP UNTIL THIS TOUR WE MADE THE JOURNEY FROM '79 TILL 5/9/81.THERE WAS JUST WAAAAYYYY TO MANY FED'S HANGING OUT. AND I REMEMBER SHORTLY BEFORE THIS THAT GARCIA SAID THAT HE WOULD NEVER SUBJECT US TO THESE ASSHOLE'S AGAIN.BECAUSE THE D.E.A MADE IT IN THE PARKING LOT PRIOR TO THIS TOUR.THIS NIGHT I BOUGHT A BACKSTAGE PASS FOR JUST ABOUT NOTHING AND IN THOSE DAY'S STICK ON PASSES GOT YOU EVERYWHERE.AND ON THIS NIGHT I WALKED AROUND A CORNER WHEN THE LIGHT'S WENT DOWN FOR SET 2 AND FOUND MYSELF WALKING TO THE STAGE WITH GARCIA AND PARRISH WE MADE SMALL TALK AND I LET THEM KNOW THE FED'S WERE OUTSIDE AND REALLY FUCKED UP SOME PEOPLE'S LIVES THEY SAID THEY WERE TOLD THERE WOULD BE NO STORM TROOPER'S OUTSIDE.THEY WERE EXTREMELY UPSET ABOUT THIS.BUT BACK TO THE MUSIC I THOUGHT 5/6/81 BLEW THIS NIGHT AWY AS WELL AS 5/4 IN PHILLY WAS KILLER. I WAS JUST HAPPY TO GET BACK TO MY HOTEL ALIVE AND NOT IN HANDCUFFS.A REAL BIG DRAG WAS COMING UP WITH BAIL TO GET MY BUDDY OUT OF JAIL.PLUS THE PEOPLE OF UNIONDALE WERE NOT TO FRIENDLY EITHER.
HEYYYYYY BECAUSE IM THE BIGGEST DEADHEAD THAT EVER LIVED< ALL MY PINIONS ARE THE CORRECT ONES< DON"T YOU NEWBIES WHO HAVE ONLY SEEN 200 SHOWS KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT MUSIC? SHESH! SO STUPID!
